# pharma_RD_workflow — AI agent instructions

Before answering questions, planning work, or writing or editing code in this repository, **read the project context document** for stack, conventions, and non-negotiable rules:

**`_bmad-output/project-context.md`**

That file is the authoritative summary of technology versions, pipeline contracts, logging, testing, security, and product constraints (e.g. decision-support positioning, human-owned pursuit language). Follow it unless the user explicitly overrides for a one-off task.

